{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/supply-theme-add-a-slideshow-to-your-product-pages","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1036,"date":"2021-07-21T00:43:12","date_gmt":"2021-07-21T00:43:12","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1036"},"modified":"2021-07-21T01:07:12","modified_gmt":"2021-07-21T01:07:12","slug":"supply-theme-add-a-slideshow-to-your-product-pages","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/supply-theme-add-a-slideshow-to-your-product-pages/","title":{"rendered":"Supply Theme: add a slideshow to your product pages"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>The Supply theme&#8217;s well known for its outstanding ease of showcasing and filtering large inventories. Store owners with large amount of products and stock certainly do benefit of Supply&#8217;s &#8220;straightforward&#8221; type of design. Anyhow, Supply&#8217;s fall short when it fails to provide a slideshow for product page images; users in this day and age are, according to studies, much more prone to scrolling than clicking. <br><br>This is where sliders come in handy, regardless of what theme or design one is after.<br><br>Bearing that in mind, in this tutorial I&#8217;ll show you how you can quick and easily add a slideshow to your Supply theme product page, all it takes is copying and pasting one single code file. <br><br>You can <a href=\"https://supply-password-is-123.myshopify.com/products/dummy-product\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">view the end result clicking here</a>. (Password: <strong>123</strong>)</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-making-a-backup-of-your-current-theme\">Making a backup of your current theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-downloading-the-files\">Downloading the files</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/supply-theme-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>Download</strong></a><strong> </strong>the files <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/supply-theme-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">clicking here.</a> (<a href=\"https://supply-password-is-123.myshopify.com/products/dummy-product\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">live preview</a> &#8211; password: <strong>123</strong>)<br><br>The complete details about the slideshow <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/supply-theme-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">can be found clicking here.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-installing-the-slideshow-code\">Installing the slideshow code </h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, navigate to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1349\" height=\"614\" class=\"wp-image-626\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code.jpg 1349w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-600x273.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-1200x546.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-768x350.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1349px) 100vw, 1349px\" /></li><li>Find a file named <strong>product-template.liquid</strong><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1004\" height=\"417\" class=\"wp-image-628\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/product-template.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/product-template.jpg 1004w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/product-template-600x249.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/product-template-768x319.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1004px) 100vw, 1004px\" /></li><li>Delete everything inside of this file. Make sure it is blank:<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1265\" height=\"548\" class=\"wp-image-630\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/blank1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/blank1.jpg 1265w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/blank1-600x260.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/blank1-1200x520.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/blank1-768x333.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1265px) 100vw, 1265px\" /></li><li>Now, inside of the .zip you downloaded, there will be a file called <strong>product-template.txt</strong>. Copy all the code inside of this file.</li><li>Paste this code you copied into <strong>product-template.liquid</strong> and save.</li><li>That is it! Your slideshow is now working and ready to use.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-customizing-your-new-slideshow-to-your-liking\">Customizing your new slideshow to your liking</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, navigate to <strong>Online Store</strong> > <strong>Themes </strong>><strong>Customize</strong>. <br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1711\" height=\"658\" class=\"wp-image-1040\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/supply1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/supply1.jpg 1711w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/supply1-850x327.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/supply1-1200x461.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/supply1-768x295.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/supply1-1536x591.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1711px) 100vw, 1711px\" /><br></li><li>At the top, from the dropdown options, select <strong>Products > default product</strong>. <br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1194\" height=\"434\" class=\"wp-image-1042\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/supply2.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/supply2.png 1194w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/supply2-850x309.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/supply2-768x279.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1194px) 100vw, 1194px\" /><br><br>Once this page loads, select <strong>product </strong>on the left.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"409\" height=\"435\" class=\"wp-image-1044\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/supply3.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br></li><li>Inside the <strong>Product </strong>menu you&#8217;ll find all available options for the Supply Slider.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-something-went-wrong-there-is-a-bug-or-i-can-t-install-it\">Something went wrong, there is a bug or I can&#8217;t install it</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>No worries at all! We&#8217;ll be more than happy to help you out. <br><br>Please send email us at <strong>ezfycode@gmail.com</strong> with your website URL and we&#8217;ll get back to you on the same day to assist you and get it installed.</p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Learn how to add a smooth slideshow to your product pages in just a few minutes. More than 20 customizable features built-in.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1049,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[154,8